<script>
    function myFunction() {
        var input, filter, ul, li, a, i, txtValue;
        input = document.getElementById("myInput");
        filter = input.value.toUpperCase();
        ul = document.getElementById("myUL");
        li = ul.getElementsByTagName("li");
        for (i = 0; i < li.length; i++) {
            a = li[i].getElementsByTagName("a")[0];
            txtValue = a.textContent || a.innerText;
            if (txtValue.toUpperCase().indexOf(filter) > -1) {
                li[i].style.display = "";
            } else {
                li[i].style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    }
</script>
 
<h1>All bootstrap icons</h1>

<input type="text" id="myInput" class="form-control"onkeyup="myFunction()" placeholder="Search Icons" title="Type in a name" >

<hr>

<ul id="myUL" class="row row-cols-3 row-cols-sm-4 row-cols-lg-6 row-cols-xl-8 list-unstyled list">

  <a>
  <div class="p-3 py-4 mb-2 bg-light text-center rounded">
  <i class="bi-{{icon}}" style="font-size: 2rem; color: cornflowerblue;"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="name text-muted text-decoration-none text-center pt-1">{{icon}}</div>
  </a>
  </li>
{% endfor%}

</ul>

function myFunction() {
    var input, filter, ul, li, a, i, txtValue;
    input = document.getElementById("myInput");
    filter = input.value.toUpperCase();
    ul = document.getElementById("myUL");
    li = ul.getElementsByTagName("li");
    for (i = 0; i < li.length; i++) {
        a = li[i].getElementsByTagName("a")[0];

        if (txtValue.toUpperCase().indexOf(filter) > -1) {
            li[i].style.display = "";
        } else {
            li[i].style.display = "none";
        }
    }
}
</script>
